# Architecture Standards

{% if profile == "mvc" %}
We adhere to the **MVC (Model-View-Controller)** pattern.

## Directory Structure
- **src/app/models/**: Data structures.
- **src/app/views/**: UI/Presentation logic.
- **src/app/controllers/**: Orchestration logic.
{% elif profile == "web" %}
We adhere to a standard Web Application structure.

## Directory Structure
- **src/backend/**: API and server logic.
- **src/frontend/**: Static assets and templates.
{% elif profile == "system" %}
We adhere to an Ansible-First automation structure.

## Directory Structure
- **ansible/roles/**: Reusable logic units.
- **scripts/**: Helper scripts.
{% endif %}

## Coding Standards
- **Type Hints**: Mandatory for all function signatures.
- **Configuration**: Use environment variables or config files.

## Source Control Standards
- **Strict Branching**: Always create a specific branch (`feat/`, `fix/`, `docs/`, `chore/`) for your work.
- **Commit Messages**: Strictly follow [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/).
